---
title: Mumbai Beef Meatballs & Onion Chutney with Cheesy Spiced Fries & Mixed Salad
description: Discover a classic fusion of Indian and modern flavours with a whole new twist! Take crispy bombay fries paired with moreish chutney-glazed beef meatballs, all the right spices and tender veggies, and you’ve got a dinner-time hit. Serve with a lush salad for a hit of freshness.

